---
title: BBQ Lemon & Herb Chicken and Summer Lamb Koftas with Wedges, Greek Style Salad and Houmous
description: Enjoy the best of the British summertime with a BBQ feast! Perfectly suited for cooking on your BBQ, this BBQ Lemon & Herb Chicken and Summer Lamb Koftas can also be just as easily prepared in your oven.
